Working Beyond Time/Space in the Imaginal Realm

Excerpts from Living Your Vision - Vital Keys to Greater Happiness, Success and Joy, Los Angeles  Intensive, June, 1995

Time/space and the Imaginal Realm are vast topics, as are the Archetypes whose assistance we need to move into, experience and work with the Imaginal Realm. In this brief discussion, Lazaris talks 
about the torus through which we can pass to move beyond space/time and into the Imaginal Realm where imagination imagines itself and creativity creates itself. This is not a complete discussion but it is a fun and enlightening overview that brings with it the flavor of this vast realm of tremendous power.

